reason: Some people don't know that Vava was renamed to Vile in the US (and I think Euro) release.  "Vile" is ambiguous enough that it should never be a descriptor, and I can think of no other character, copyright, or artist that uses this.
Alternate spelling, used by several dubs of the anime.
We originally used the former, but then it changed and wasn't aliased.
Both tags refer to Caster's knife (from Fate/Stay Night).
